3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses a neural network based feature detector and discusses training it using a large amount of 3D world capture data.
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper mentions generating labeled 2D images from a photo-realistic 3D dataset, which involves graphics techniques.
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper uses deep neural networks for feature detection, which is a common technique in AI research.
